{"tid":949671,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【有計傾】中國計劃聖誕前再買入200萬噸美國大豆","createTime":"2018-12-21T03:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T06:42:40.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ef197e51fe000fa63fab23e24153e8ea6818d8","tid":949671,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181221/_2018122111055871272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181221%2F_2018122111055871272.jpg&h=0478fe4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述兩名消息人士報道，中國計劃在聖誕節前進行第三輪美國大豆採購，再購買超過200萬噸美國大豆，將會是國家主席習近平與美國總統特朗普月初在阿根廷會談後，中國近期第三輪購買大豆行動，亦令今個月美國出口到中國的大豆數目，增至超過500萬噸。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普和中國國家主席習近平於12月1日會晤，雙方決定貿易戰休戰90天，期間兩國將進行談判以解決貿易爭端。此後，中國在停止購買美國大豆六個月後恢復採購。<br />\n<br />\n然而，美國大豆期貨價格近期不斷下跌，因為到目前為止中國的購買量微不足道。<br />\n<br />\n美國去年向中國出口大豆3,100多萬噸，價值122.5億美元，佔美國大豆出口總量的近60%。"},{"pid":"60be68601fe9becf5e9e0b83f54d6470e3b55ed0","tid":949671,"uid":13008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9ef197e51fe000fa63fab23e24153e8ea6818d8","tid":949671,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181221/_2018122111055871272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181221%2F_2018122111055871272.jpg&h=0478fe4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述兩名消息人士報道，中國計劃在聖誕節前進行第三輪美國大豆採購，再購買超過200萬噸美國大豆，將會是國家主席習近平與美國總統特朗普月初在阿根廷會談後，中國近期第三輪購買大豆行動，亦令今個月美國出口到中國的大豆數目，增至超過500萬噸。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普和中國國家主席習近平於12月1日會晤，雙方決定貿易戰休戰90天，期間兩國將進行談判以解決貿易爭端。此後，中國在停止購買美國大豆六個月後恢復採購。<br />\n<br />\n然而，美國大豆期貨價格近期不斷下跌，因為到目前為止中國的購買量微不足道。<br />\n<br />\n美國去年向中國出口大豆3,100多萬噸，價值122.5億美元，佔美國大豆出口總量的近60%。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab86794ebcb2b49b024dc8b37774d814f81f3fb1","tid":949671,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"先打大豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再打汽車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7cc26716724e074bd636d4384e3b297107f578","tid":949671,"uid":58913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0d1385089012c6deae00719f611ac0d73b5312","tid":949671,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:38:12.000Z","msg":"大豆外交"},{"pid":"6bb9db8513ed5f5580f8723967f559a7dac38b25","tid":949671,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"入定貨再來戰"},{"pid":"af7f5eb7ca0be316e33ba6b40798126ae3cbb847","tid":949671,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"幅圖好正，想跳入個豆池到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cbba896c123e95c06ac0b858246cbc88c30b32","tid":949671,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T03:57:15.000Z","msg":"又話食草"},{"pid":"a4c3a320dae1bcea7c305455a1c97f71bf13ed6b","tid":949671,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:19:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家, 無骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1061a231253903d87af0789b22e420b0331f30","tid":949671,"uid":159313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zVl5Atf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzVl5Atf.jpg&h=bcc550f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44919c9d23d74ff2b10def123eb63b11